snippet.title: ModBot
snippet.description:
Follow me on this channel where I will be talking about 3d printers and just about anything tech. You can expect news updates, tutorials, mods, product reviews, as well as a wide variety of other videos!

My goal is to use my love for technology to create videos that will be both informational and (hopefully) entertaining for everyone to watch :).

The opinions are that of my own, and I welcome you to debate and add your own opinions\experiences.

If interested in having a product reviewed please email me at dopesoner930@gmail.com
